MapAttack is an application comprising of an interactive map displaying a number of several attacks (verbal attacks, police attacks etc.) focused on these which took place in the broader region of Greece. Built with MEAN stack. Influenced by http://map.crisis-scape.net/

Visit the application here:
https://map-attack.herokuapp.com/

Test it as an authorized user using the following credentials:
username: testuser
password: test

